HAL bridge function:
 take component, uri command param (multiples?)
 bridge = active side = connects, creates/verifies comp, subscribes
 on startup either connect to existing local halcomp, or create from remote comp
 states: discovery,connecting, verified, mismatch, up/updates flowing

options:name, cmduri updateuri (instance # - sd?)

 connecting: describe until reply
	     verify local comp OR create according to describe
	     compile local comp
	     set up updates

 updates: in+inout only
